-- Center Parcs Said to Plan Bond Investor Meetings
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n   a n d   H a n n a h   B e n j a m i n
-- 2012-02-07T09:31:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-07/center-parcs-said-to-plan-bond-investor-meetings.html
Center Parcs plans to meet bond
investors ahead of a sale of class A and class B bonds in
pounds, according to two people with knowledge of the
arrangements.  Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc,  Barclays Capital , HSBC
Holdings Plc and Lloyds Banking Group Plc have been hired to
organize the meetings.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Martin at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net  